➜黑蒜仔牛肉粒的家常做法，蒜香浓郁，美味可口
http://www.sohu.com/a/414515306_119132	10792
<p class="ql-align-justify">大蒜向来以调味品出现在厨房，多数人不知的是，把大蒜直接做菜烹炒，味道美极了。今天给大家带来一道黑蒜仔牛肉粒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200823/f060655aee97445ba224a01f773f1cc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">准备食材：牛肉300g 蒜瓣100g 洋葱50g 鸡蛋1个 西红柿1个 胡萝卜1个 胡椒粉2g 香菜5g</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/0c094af57c7a4f63b42e82347fdc56f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">制作方法：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、首先把牛肉切丁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/a157a40a622847d5a8692420a7e7a6f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、分别把洋葱、西红柿、胡萝卜、香菜切碎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200823/397adfe9f3044047879432b14df2caf7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、把切好的牛肉装进碗中放入2g盐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200823/1345b17701604116bc92f5afd93575a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、放入1g白胡椒粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200823/5ca82d0d6c644125b37fa0a668425b52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、放入半勺料酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200823/c0b9083f26c34512be3c5f025f3b5833.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6、放入半勺生抽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/4c6c514b23df442ba92a59a1bf12b231.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7、放入1勺淀粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/b8a85843adfd4888ab27cd0acf25add2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8、在磕入一个鸡蛋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200823/d156c30fe3d64ba7891d0f6db40947fb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">9、放入2勺大豆油</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200823/3714eb2df6cd4b878e8c858d907712f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">10、放入切好的辅料用手抓匀腌制15分钟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200823/444e8ad5098443099c00d1fe4ded93f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">11、油锅烧热，油温5成热放入蒜瓣炸至金黄捞出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/be1ad2d41fb544b28efc89c41af32310.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">12、把辅料挑出（我没挑净）放入刚才炸蒜的油锅炸制断生捞出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200823/afe45b349f9548feae65982ead513eff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">13、锅留底油，放入炸好的牛肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200823/f9c1ea85426f4c91aa0ba6db5efda0ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">14、放入少许生抽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/78f5e968bf734034833fa4f5cc3920c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">15、放入半勺料酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200823/7bd92963c374437199b4735aa0973d27.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">16、放入耗油</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200823/3809f585971e47faac0cd9169f09f0de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">17、放入1g白胡椒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200823/f898ab5cd7bb49d497309b1a5347cc04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">18、再放入炸好的蒜瓣翻炒均匀即可</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200823/4aecc80e4f8248c1a086f8eafcb9dd9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">19、出锅，制作完成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200823/8f64cfb24da44140ac18cc48c0161d8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>